parameters:
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Mother, I will definitely become a direct-line mage... just
like you...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lady Lucia, you were here after all. What's the matter?

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehe... It's the same as always. Mother won't pass on the
direct-line power to me.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] How about you? Do you think you can master the Azure Magic?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes. The training is tough, but somehow I'll manage to learn
it.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I see. That's good to hear.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Luuna, I want to go to the lower world again.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] The lower world wasn't peaceful, but there were countries like
the Kingdom of Lyubel and the Free Country of Moduna that shared our
values.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I don't know about the perpetually neutral Moduna, but Lyubel
was a country that had renounced war. Prince Reenu and Lady Lucia
would make a lovely couple~.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] But Prince Reenu might be a bit of my type~.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Hehe, but too bad, I have Mido after all.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Hehe... So Lady Lucia really likes Mr. Mido.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Yes. Luuna, let's eat together once you bring the lunch.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Now then, what shall we eat first~?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] What is it~? We're close, aren't we~? Don't hold back.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Can I call you... big sister?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I've been so happy since Lady Lucia picked me up. You've
treated me just like a real sister, and I just... I'm sorry for saying
something weird.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Luuna, call me "big sister." I wasn't wrong in choosing you as
a court magician.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I'll call you big sister when I feel like it~.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Ahaha, what's with that~? You're the one who brought it up~.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Let's eat our lunch quickly before it gets cold.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lady Lucia, I'm happy to be with you.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Me too, Luuna. I'm very happy right now.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] This is... a memory of Noah and me from the past...
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Luuna, the floating continent is beautiful at night too.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] It's strange to think that there are billions... no, more
magicians in this world. Those with the qualities of a blue magician
are even fewer.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] When I was little, I decided when I met Luuna that it was my
role to extend Luuna's exceptional magical talents.
\C[29][Noah]\C[0] No, that's not all. I think Luuna is...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I also feel the same about Noah...
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Luuna, Noah. You two are always together. Hehe...
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] When will you two become lovers?
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lady Lucia, did something happen today?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Father is trying to form an alliance with Valentina.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] You know how the elite magicians from Valentina have come to
Jupiterino and are rampaging as they please, right?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] But Father can't stand up to Valentina.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Even though so many of our own people are being killed...

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Mother, who is a direct-line magician, also values the
relationship with Valentina.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] As the princess of Jupiterino, it's frustrating... sad...

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] If only I could become a direct-line magician... I could
protect this country.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] No... It's just that I've never seen you cry before, Lady
Lucia. I am proud of you for shedding tears for the people.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lady Luuna, Her Majesty the Empress... I believe Lady Reicia
must have some plan in mind.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Is that so? But Mother won't give me any answers.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I want to inherit the direct-line power from Mother as soon as
possible... and then those guys...

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes. Lady Lucia, I'm sure that one day you will become a
direct-line magician.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Lady Lucia, when that time comes, Luuna and I will lend you our
strength.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Exactly. I too will master the essence of blue magic.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Thank you both. I will definitely become a direct-line
magician.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] The three of us will always be together.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Why would the Mirror of Truth reveal such information to me...
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] It's been a while since Lucia shed tears for the people.

\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Well, now Lucia is a legendary magician. People change when they
hold immense power.

\C[29][Noah]\C[0] Suddenly, I was overcome with sleep and saw Luuna and Lucia in a
dream. I thought maybe Luuna was having the same dream.

\C[24][Becky]\C[0] The Mirror of Truth is amazing. It's incredible that its magic
reached Noah even from afar.

\C[24][Cain]\C[0] Noah, that's not really what you came here for, is it? You just
wanted an excuse to talk to Luuna, didn't you?
\C[24][Cain]\C[0] I knew it. You really do like Luuna, don't you?
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Luuna, you should respond to his love call.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Hehe... Noah, let's talk more when we get back.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Now, let's get out of here.
